<p><b>IBM mainframe utility programs</b> are supplied with <a href="/wiki/IBM" title="IBM">IBM</a> <a href="/wiki/Mainframe_computer" title="Mainframe computer">mainframe</a> <a href="/wiki/Operating_system" title="Operating system">operating systems</a> such as <a href="/wiki/MVS" title="MVS">MVS</a> to carry out various tasks associated with <a href="/wiki/Data_set_(IBM_mainframe)" title="Data set (IBM mainframe)">datasets</a>, etc.</p>
<table class="navbox" cellspacing="0" style="width:30em;float:right;;">
